%% SBOM validation pipeline — eight-stage sequence
%% Companion to docs/adr/0007-sbom-validation-architecture.md
%%
%% Render with: any Mermaid renderer (GitHub native, mermaid-cli, mermaid.live).
%% Each stage is a participant. Notes mark short-circuit exits with their HTTP status.

sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client
    participant ASGI as MaxBodySizeMiddleware
    participant API as POST /api/sboms/upload
    participant S1 as Stage 1<br/>Ingress guard
    participant S2 as Stage 2<br/>Format & version
    participant S3 as Stage 3<br/>Structural schema
    participant S4 as Stage 4<br/>Semantic
    participant S5 as Stage 5<br/>Cross-ref integrity
    participant S6 as Stage 6<br/>Security checks
    participant S7 as Stage 7<br/>NTIA elements
    participant S8 as Stage 8<br/>Signature
    participant Q as Celery scan queue

    Client->>ASGI: POST /api/sboms/upload<br/>multipart bytes
    ASGI-->>Client: 413 if Content-Length > MAX_UPLOAD_BYTES
    ASGI->>API: scope, receive (size-guarded)

    API->>S1: ctx(raw_bytes)
    Note over S1: size ≤ 50 MB (uploaded)<br/>≤ 200 MB (decompressed)<br/>UTF-8 / BOM / decompression-bomb
    alt stage 1 errors
        S1-->>API: report(error, http=413)
        API-->>Client: 413 SBOM_VAL_E001..E006
    else stage 1 ok
        S1->>S2: ctx(text)
    end

    Note over S2: structural fingerprint —<br/>SPDX vs CycloneDX × json/xml/yaml/tag-value
    alt format unknown / ambiguous / unsupported
        S2-->>API: report(error, http=415)
        API-->>Client: 415 SBOM_VAL_E010..E013
    else stage 2 ok
        S2->>S3: ctx(spec, version, encoding)
    end

    Note over S3: vendored JSON Schema /<br/>XSD per (spec, version)<br/>defusedxml + lxml safe-parse<br/>aggregate up to 100 errors
    alt parse failure
        S3-->>API: report(error, http=400)
        API-->>Client: 400 SBOM_VAL_E020..E024
    else schema violations
        S3-->>API: report(error, http=422)
        API-->>Client: 422 SBOM_VAL_E025..E029
    else stage 3 ok
        S3->>S4: ctx(parsed_dict)
    end

    Note over S4: SPDX: SPDXID, namespace,<br/>dataLicense, licence-expression,<br/>checksum length, timestamp,<br/>DESCRIBES relationship<br/>CycloneDX: serialNumber URN,<br/>bom-ref uniqueness, PURL,<br/>CPE 2.3, hash length, timestamp
    alt semantic violations
        S4-->>API: report(error, http=422)
        API-->>Client: 422 SBOM_VAL_E040..E057
    else stage 4 ok
        S4->>S5: ctx(internal_model)
    end

    Note over S5: dependency / relationship<br/>refs resolve; cycles → warning;<br/>orphans → info
    alt unresolved refs
        S5-->>API: report(error, http=422)
        API-->>Client: 422 SBOM_VAL_E070..E073
    else stage 5 ok (cycles / orphans = warnings)
        S5->>S6: ctx(internal_model)
    end

    Note over S6: JSON depth ≤ 64,<br/>array ≤ 1e6, string ≤ 64 KB;<br/>XML DTD/external entity forbidden;<br/>YAML safe-only;<br/>prototype-pollution keys rejected
    alt security guard tripped
        S6-->>API: report(error, http=400 or 413)
        API-->>Client: 400/413 SBOM_VAL_E080..E089
    else stage 6 ok
        S6->>S7: ctx(internal_model)
    end

    Note over S7: NTIA minimum elements:<br/>supplier, name, version, id,<br/>relationship, author, timestamp.<br/>Default = warnings;<br/>?strict=true → errors
    alt NTIA strict + missing
        S7-->>API: report(error, http=422)
        API-->>Client: 422 SBOM_VAL_E100..E106
    else stage 7 default
        S7->>S8: ctx(internal_model, ntia_warnings)
    end

    Note over S8: Feature-flagged.<br/>CycloneDX JSF / SPDX external sig.<br/>Default OFF in v1.
    alt signature flag on AND signature invalid
        S8-->>API: report(error, http=422)
        API-->>Client: 422 SBOM_VAL_E110..E112
    else stage 8 ok / flag off
        S8->>API: ctx(internal_model, warnings, info)
    end

    API->>Q: enqueue_scan(internal_model)
    Q-->>API: job_id
    API-->>Client: 202 Accepted<br/>{ job_id, warnings, info }
